sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Frontend as HTML Frontend
    participant Backend as Flask Backend
    participant Miragic as Miragic AI API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    
    User->>Frontend: Upload human+cloth images
    Frontend->>Backend: POST /api/tryon/single<br/>{humanImage, clothImage}
    Backend->>Miragic: POST /virtual-try-on<br/>X-API-Key + files
    Miragic-->>Backend: {jobId}
    Backend->>Backend: Poll /virtual-try-on/{jobId}
    alt Job COMPLETED
        Miragic-->>Backend: {status: COMPLETED, processedUrl}
        Backend->>DB: INSERT try_on_history
        Backend-->>Frontend: {success:true, processedUrl}
        Frontend->>User: Display result image
    else FAILED/TIMEOUT
        Backend-->>Frontend: {success:false, error}
        Frontend->>User: Error message
    end
    
    Note over Backend,Miragic: Polling every 2s, timeout 60s<br/>Fallback: Local image overlay

